Package: refclass
Type: Package
Title: Refactor of R reference classes
Version: 0.1
Author: Robert Krzyzanowski <technoguyrob@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Robert Krzyzanowski <technoguyrob@gmail.com>
Authors@R: c(person("Robert", "Krzyzanowski",
    email = "technoguyrob@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: R's implementation of reference classes is notorious for its
    inscrutability. This package attempts to refactor reference classes using
    more sane development practices.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.2)
License: MIT
Suggests:
    testthat
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(wrap = FALSE)
